column5: I went out on cedar lake just south of minden today. 4" - 6" of black ice and about 1" of white. Fished for a couple of hours and missed one nice fish. I will be out next weekend if anyone wants to join me. Cheers Jeff
Thanks for the report Jeff!!!  You win the prize for first ice report!  Sinker
good job jeff... i was out today on around 3" of good ice and got 2 splake around 15". its good to be back on the ice!!
WTG.  Thanks for the ice report.
As per my post on "hook ups" I want to fish,but am totally booked up this upcoming weekend.Let me know about any other upcoming trips.
